‎APEL EȘUAT

611
00:42:07,120 --> 00:42:07,960
‎Futu-i!

612
00:42:23,360 --> 00:42:25,160
‎Sigur ești bine, dragă?

613
00:42:25,920 --> 00:42:27,080
‎Ies puțin afară.

614
00:42:27,160 --> 00:42:28,480
‎Afară? Acum?

615
00:42:28,560 --> 00:42:32,400
‎Da, nu mă simt bine. Ies la o plimbare.

616
00:42:33,400 --> 00:42:35,040
‎Sigur totul e bine?

617
00:42:35,120 --> 00:42:37,040
‎Sunt bine. Nu stau mult.

618
00:43:09,400 --> 00:43:10,600
‎SUNĂ…

619
00:43:21,520 --> 00:43:23,760
‎Rahat! Haide!

620
00:43:28,640 --> 00:43:30,520
‎Poate te-a afectat accidentul.

621
00:43:31,560 --> 00:43:33,520
‎- Vei răci.
‎- Sunt bine.

622
00:43:34,080 --> 00:43:36,160
‎- Ar trebui să urci.
‎- Nu.

623
00:43:36,240 --> 00:43:37,280
‎Urcă în mașină!

624
00:44:07,680 --> 00:44:09,400
‎Întoarce-te acum!

625
00:44:29,760 --> 00:44:31,200
‎Nu-ți fac nimic!

626
00:45:01,960 --> 00:45:02,800
‎Nu.

627
00:45:05,160 --> 00:45:06,040
‎Târfă!

628
00:45:08,280 --> 00:45:09,200
‎Futu-i!

629
00:45:09,920 --> 00:45:12,200
‎Târfă!

630
00:45:13,320 --> 00:45:17,720
‎Futu-i! Târfă! Futu-i!

631
